name: Rascal the Teddy
description:
Rascal is a super-cute teddy bear, with attitude. He has a bit of body art on his bottom, and loves to relax in the sun, showing off his heart for all to see!

Rascal was created using a pattern from Funky Friends Factory.

Fabric used is new fleece. Rascal is stuffed with polyfill. His scarf is handknitted in 100% Australian cotton.

name: Mama Goo's Tote
description:
A practical tote bag, made using upholstery-weight fabric for the outer, and lined with 100% cotton.

The fabric handles make carrying the bag comfortable.

There are strip pockets on the lining.

Size: 
- approx 30cm wide and 40cm high, with a flat bottom about 6cm wide
- handles are long enough to hang on your shoulder, but also short enough to hold in your hand and not have the bag drag on the ground

name: Mug Rugs (Fabric Coasters) - Pack of 4
description:
100% cotton mug rugs are a great way to protect your furniture.

These mug rugs have cotton batting in them, and are lightly quilted.

Just throw them in the washing machine when they are dirty, then iron them when they are dry, and they will be as good as new!

(Please note the mug in the photo is not included)

name: Knitted Cotton Dishcloths
description: We're back! Be environmentally friendly - don't use disposable dishcloths, use dishcloths that you can use time and time again. 100% cotton, and handknitted, these dishcloths can simply be thrown into the washing machine when dirty. They will last for years! They are very gentle on your crockery and cutlery - and anything else you wash up. With the texture from being knitted, they will also remove all but the most stubborn dirt. This is a set of 3 small (160mm x 180mm) dishcloths.

name: Handmade Cards - Pack of 5
description:
A pack of 5 handmade cards, with envelopes.
 
The cards contain a blank paper insert, so you can add your own personalised greeting and message.
 
No card is the same, unless you specifically ask for duplicates.
 
The cards also may vary in size.
 
Choose a theme - options include Birthday, Christmas, Congratulations, Mixed.
 
Photo shows examples only. Actual cards will differ.
